    <description>Data Access Library for reading and writing files in commonly used formats
    including: R, Matlab, Text (CSV, delimited, fixed width), matrix market, stata.
    
    Part of the Numerics.NET.</description>
    <summary>Numerics.NET Data Access Library.</summary>
